title: 2002 Hyundai Santro LP CNG On RC 74999
content:
Selling Hyundai Santro 1.1 LP euro-II for 75,000/- only.

Price is competitive as compared to similar cars on sale. 

It has low running cost, maintenance cost, very low kms run. 

Below are complete details:
- Purchase Date: August 5th, 2002.

- Single Owner and Self driven in city.

- Engine in good condition and has no issues till now. No engine work done till now.

- Original paint

- Regular service done at every 5000 kms. Records available 

- Color: Prime beige (light golden metallic)
- Power steering.

- wheel balancing and alignment done periodically.
- Under body anti rust coating done from MGF Hyundai on first car service in 2002.
- Teflon coating done from MGF Hyundai on first car service in 2002.
- Seat Covers, Panasonic Music system, Central Locking all purchased from MGF Hyundai at the time of car purchase.
- Few scratches on left side and on bumper. 
- New tires: Yokohama (Made in Japan) tube less. costing Rs. 12000/-. One spare Tyre is original one (Bridgestone) that came with car.
- Full Insurance (comprehensive) till January 2016.
- CNG fitted from govt. approved dealer. Not driven much on CNG as don't get time to fill CNG as station has long lines.

- no problem till now in CNG kit of tomasetto achille original from Argentina.
- CNG on RC. CNG kit verification plate installed and valid till 2017.

- All papers maintained up to date (Insurance/RC/Pollution). 
- Kilometers driven till date is 48000 kms. It is less because it is used only in city 125 kms per week from home to office and was not used for 1-2 year as I was out of Delhi.

- Nylon car body cover used for only 5-10 times.
- Car always kept in covered garage at home and in covered parking in office.
- Transfer of title is must.

- Central locking with battery backup and sensors. However wire of it was unplugged with battery. 
- Battery replaced in 2013. Have warranty card of it.
- chilling Air Condition recently serviced.


If you are interested, please view photos and then we can meet at some location convenient to both parties.

Location I can meet: Akshardham, Mayur Vihar Phase 1/ Phase 2, Patparganj, IP Extension, Laxmi Nagar, Ganesh Nagar, Pandav Nagar, Mother Dairy, Shakarpur, Noida..

Request you to not waste both people time if you are not seriously interested. 

Thanks.
